title: Home Price Predictor
description: Developed and optimized a statistical modeling on 2.2M+ real estate listings to predict prices. Created a valuation framework comparing listed vs. predicted prices, identifying 10.5% of properties as undervalued.

title: Spotify Popularity Analysis
description: Performed EDA on 100,000+ Spotify tracks to identify key audio features linked to song popularity.

title: Power Outages
description: Performed statistical analysis and predictive modeling on U.S. power outage data (2000–2016) to identify key factors affecting major outages and forecast regional energy consumption to help utility companies improve outage response.

title: PSCL Interactive Dashboard
description: Developed an interactive Looker Studio dashboard with Pitching—including tables for max and average velocity and spin rate, pie charts for pitch distribution, and bar graphs for pitch outcomes—and Hitting Metrics, such as tables highlighting max exit velocity, average launch angle, and average exit velocity by player and pitch type. This dashboard provided a user-friendly interface for coaches and players to track their performances and showcase their abilities to college scouts.
